from machinelogic import Machine, ActuatorGroup

### Configuration ###

# If the configuration changes, please update the code below, and ensure that the names match.

my_controller__1 = machine.get_machine_motion("Controller #1")

# Configured Actuators
my_new_actuator__3_ = machine.get_actuator("New actuator (3)")
my_new_actuator__4_ = machine.get_actuator("New actuator (4)")
my_new_actuator__5_ = machine.get_actuator("New actuator (5)")
my_new_actuator = machine.get_pneumatic("New actuator")

my_new_actuator__2_ = machine.get_pneumatic("New actuator (2)")
# Configured Inputs
my_fi_n_zone_1 = machine.get_input("FIn zone 1")

### Program ###

# Documentation can be found at https://vention.io/resources/guides/machinelogic-python-programming-514
